### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/auth
@appUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@origin = http://localhost:3000

### 0. Verificar Salud de la API
GET {{appUrl}}/health

### 0.1 Probar Analíticas (Protegido - Debería dar 401 si no hay login)
GET {{appUrl}}/analytics

### 1. Probar Registro (Sign Up)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sign-up/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Referer: http://localhost:3000/

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123",
    "name": "Prueba Usuario"
}

### 2. Probar Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/sign-in/email
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Referer: http://localhost:3000/

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Verificar Sesión Actual
GET {{baseUrl}}/get-session

### 4. Cerrar Sesión (Sign Out)
POST {{baseUrl}}/sign-out
Content-Type: application/json
Origin: http://localhost:3000
Referer: http://localhost:3000/

{}